JOHANNESBURG - The flamboyant choreographer and Idols SA judge Somizi Mhlongo has asked his boyfriend Mohale Motaung to marry him and he said yes. The pair has been on a romantic getaway in Europe, they posted pictures of themselves touring Paris, the city of Love, which is where Mhlongo reportedly popped the question. They posted loving pictures of themselves at the iconic Pont De L'archeveche where they secured a locket to symbolize their love. On Monday, Mhlongo posted a video of the diamond ring that sparkled in the sunlight with the caption: "It’s a Big YESSSSS. it’s a golden ticket." It’s a Big YESSSSS. it’s a golden ticket. #MCM #MCE A post shared by  Somizi (@somizi) on My bestie @mohale_77 life is sweeter with u by my side A post shared by  Somizi (@somizi) on Locked. A post shared by  Somizi (@somizi) on Being in the moment. With my buddy who just happen to be my lover. @mohale_77 A post shared by  Somizi (@somizi) on A post shared by  Somizi (@somizi) on A post shared by Somizi (@somizi) on eNCA